Package smarthome.persistence.mem

Class SensorRepositoryMemImpl

java.lang.Object
smarthome.persistence.mem.SensorRepositoryMemImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
IRepository<SensorId, Sensor>, ISensorRepository
public class SensorRepositoryMemImpl extends Object implements ISensorRepository
The SensorRepositoryMemImpl class represents a repository for managing Sensor entities. It provides methods to save, retrieve, and manipulate Sensor objects. This repository is backed by an in-memory HashMap data structure. SensorId representing the identity of Sensor entities. Sensor representing Sensor entities.
